{"tid":1091280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑醫生專業失德可以點投訴","createTime":"2019-04-04T04:36:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T04:37:19.000Z","uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a4b0388987cdae683b78f70512cb616274acb3b3","tid":1091280,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T04:36:12.000Z","msg":"今朝我個朋友話我知佢有發燒就睇醫生<br />\n做左快速測試真係中左流感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住問佢除左發燒仲有邊度唔舒服<br />\n佢話好似有小小喉嚨痛咁咯<br />\n但冇咳又冇頭痛又冇乜其他野<br />\n點知醫生話冇併發症唔駛食特敏福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但唔食一陣有事點算 好似好多人中流感死左<br />\n呀條醫生夠膽死話每個人抵抗力唔同，食左未必有咩特效wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實啲醫生到底有冇學過識唔識醫架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43dc135970810119a0f401c6e7c2d2183359ac3e","tid":1091280,"uid":26385,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T04:37:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}